channel.title: Interleaved RSS Feed
channel.description: This is an interleaved feed of the most recent entries from each RSS source, skipping any feeds with errors.

item.title: DeSantis Brings Reality Check to Media Over Kamala Lovefest: She's 'Vapid,' 'Owns' All Biden's Policies
Biden calls for Supreme Court term limits, code of conduct, limits on presidential immunity
item.description: President Biden is calling for Supreme Court term limits, a code of conduct, and new limits on presidential immunity in a Monday op-ed.

item.title: Trump, Harris Enter 99-Day Sprint After Historic Swap Out
item.description: Barely a week ago, a sense of inevitability hung over the U.S. presidential election, so the Democrats orchestrated a swap out to Vice President Kamala Harris, moving the goal posts as Donald Trump's campaign was scoring too many points on President Joe Biden.

item.title: Watch As Venezuelans Show Their Willpower to Vote Out Strongman Maduro in Presidential Election
Trump's legal wins seem to simplify upcoming general election campaign schedule
item.description: Former President Trump has had a number of legal victories in recent weeks, pausing the majority of cases that could have complicated his campaigning.

item.title: Biden Unveils Plan for Supreme Court Term Limits, Ethics Code
item.description: President Joe Biden is unveiling a long-expected proposal for changes at the U.S. Supreme Court, calling on Congress to establish term limits and an ethics code for the court's nine justices.

item.title: WATCH: CNN's Scott Jennings Blows Up the Narrative of Former Harris Spokesperson in Mere Seconds
Harris claims Biden fit to continue in office, despite more than 80 documented encounters in past year
item.description: President Biden and Vice President Harris had more than 80 documented encounters in the past year, while Harris defended the president's mental acuity.

item.title: JD Vance Responds to Jennifer Aniston's IVF Comment
item.description: Former President Donald Trump's running mate, J.D. Vance, responded to a comment made by "Friends" star Jennifer Aniston after the Ohio senator claimed that "childless cat ladies" run the United States.

item.title: Paris Olympics Organizers Apologize for Opening Ceremony Fiasco, and It's As Lame As You'd Expect
Trump rallygoer scared to attend future Trump events, despite Secret Service urging they move inside
item.description: Former President Trump supporter Valerie McGregor, of Plum, Pennsylvania, spoke out about her experience at Trump's Butler rally and how the Secret Service director should have been long gone before her resignation.

item.title: Gore Endorses Harris For President
item.description: Former Vice President Al Gore joined on Sunday a growing list of Democrats in endorsing Vice President Kamala Harris for president.

item.title: Trump Shooter Planned to Use Explosives As 'Diversion' to Cover Escape, FBI Still Doesn't Know Motive
'So-called expert bureaucrats': Fishermen rip Sen Warren's new plan to 'silence' them
item.description: Americaâ€™s seafood leaders are pushing back on new plans from Democrats on Capitol Hill to revive the Chevron doctrine, which fishermen say threatens their livelihoods.

item.title: Trump Jr.: Google Hiding Father's Assassination Attempt
item.description: Donald Trump Jr. on Sunday accused Google of "intentional election interference" because its "Autocomplete" tool doesn't include the attempted assassination of his father, former President Donald Trump, in its results.
